Fairly OddParents - Season 9 - Episode 11 (WEB-DL - XviD)
---------------------------------------------------------

Embark on hilarity with Timmy, Cosmo, Wanda and Poof. See Timmy with his
magical dog, Sparky, watch Cosmo do his usual damage when he acts as a
genie, help Timmy's Dad be the best Squirrely Scout leader, and stop
Crocker from turning Sparky against Timmy. Face Poof's terrible twos
while Foop has his terrific twos in The Terrible Twosome, and in App Trap,
Timmy's smartphone tries to take over his life! The laughs continue when
Crocker captures Mom thinking she's a magical Breakfast Troll, Foop is
Vicky's anti-fairy godparent and together they try to destroy the fairies,
Chet Ubetcha quits and Dad takes over (nearly destroying Dimmsdale), and
Timmy's basement comes to life while Mom and Dad are at a fake spa. In
Finding Emo, Timmy tries to impress a new girl, Two and a Half Babies
has Foop and Poof paired on a school project, Timmy wishes his dad's
life was an action movie, Cosmo feuds with a gopher, and so much more
in over 3 hours of magical mayhem!

Produced by Billionfold, Frederator Incorporated and Nickelodeon Productions.


Timmy Turner is an average kid - sort of. He's an only child with oblivious
parents. But luckily he has Cosmo and Wanda, his wacky fairy godparents who
help him hide from evil babysitters, do homework and much more craziness!
